  "body": "The Ethermine team tried to mine ETC blocks using Besu and got the following error: \n\n```\n2020-05-07 07:03:40.473+00:00 | pool-9-thread-44 | WARN  | MainnetTransactionProcessor | Invalid transaction: transaction nonce 2 does not match sender account nonce 1.\n2020-05-07 07:03:55.783+00:00 | pool-9-thread-44 | WARN  | MainnetBlockBodyValidator | Invalid block: state root mismatch (expected=0x540e2c70eb2b872376e7b70352850c007a305a60791f0f67e840034dc5355896, actual=0x589b0449062c924ba6b18a15c01b9ed705e83af1574f550f56e146cc46310ffe)\n2020-05-07 07:03:55.783+00:00 | pool-9-thread-44 | ERROR | BlockMiner | Illegal block mined, could not be imported to local chain.\n```\n\nWe should investigate this and come up with a fix. \n\nBesu build: `besu/v1.4.5-dev-f39fbc56/linux-x86_64/openjdk-java-11` \n\n\nCLI: \n\n```\ncommand=/home/xxx/besu-1.4.5-SNAPSHOT/bin/besu\n --network=classic\n --data-path=/besudata/\n --sync-mode=FAST\n --miner-enabled\n --miner-coinbase=0xdf7d7e053933b5cc24372f878c90e62dadad5d42\n --min-gas-price=1000000000000\n --rpc-http-enabled\n --rpc-http-host=0.0.0.0\n --rpc-http-cors-origins=*\n --host-whitelist=*\n --target-gas-limit=10000000\n --pruning-enabled\n --max-peers=50\n```",
